title: New: Fictonian – Full Circle Influence
body:
Rather epic debut song/video combo from **Fictonian**, for _Full Circle Influence_.

Think Tame Impala wooziness with the underlying suggestion that perhaps they’ll move toward a more commercially friendly sound. In truth, who knows, their next single could be a three minute chart stormer, or a seven minute sprawl, centred around a killer guitar solo, they’re really leaving their options open.
